javax.jdo.metadata

Interface MemberMetadata

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Metadata
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    FieldMetadata, PropertyMetadata

    public interface MemberMetadata
extends Metadata
    Represents a field/property in a class/persistent-interface.

    3.0
